name: Other Portrait Series - OP_1078
description:
Visual images from a contemporary art installation where human & machine exchanged information.

Humankind will be an extension to machines. As once wheel was an extension to our legs. Like the computer was an extension to our minds.

All visuals here created by participants of an interactive art exhibition through tracking their eyes as they paint their portraits.

Over 200 pieces will be included in the Other Portrait Series.
